<p>Neighborhoods like Indian Trail and Montgomery Road areas feature larger lots and homes that often benefit from larger solar systems and zoned HVAC systems due to their size. The established neighborhoods around Aurora University and near the Fox River offer a mix of home styles and ages, requiring customized approaches to both solar and HVAC solutions. Eastern Aurora neighborhoods closer to Naperville often have higher property values and energy-conscious homeowners who particularly benefit from premium solar and HVAC systems that add significant home value while reducing utility costs.</p>

